              </div>
              <div class="form-text">Conversion runs only for export/DOCX placeholders. Raw answers stay unchanged.</div>
              <div class="form-text">Branching examples: <code>ifelse(num(value) >= 90, "A", "B")</code> or <code>caseof(value, "excellent", 4, "good", 3, "fair", 2, 0)</code>.</div>
