                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" id="btnAddCalcFieldDependency"><i class="bi bi-diagram-3 me-1"></i>Add Dependency</button>
                  </div>
                </div>
                <div class="form-text">Select a field, then insert <code>answers.&lt;fieldId&gt;</code> into formula or append its ID to dependencies.</div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-text">Calculated fields are auto-updated and read-only in Report Instance. Dependencies must reference existing non-visual field IDs.</div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-12">
              <div class="d-flex flex-wrap gap-3 border rounded p-2 bg-light">
                <div class="form-check m-0">
                  <input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" id="fieldEditorRequired">
                  <label class="form-check-label" for="fieldEditorRequired">Required</label>
